history.content: All my non-CS friends eventually get into CS170 since some ppl will drop after several weeks. But situation might change depending on each semester.

Right now I'm waitlisted on both eec106a and I want to take 149, but I'm at the unit cap (enrolled in BMOE bootcamp) so I can't enroll in it until phase 2. I was wondering if it would be a good idea to drop 170 to be on the 149 waitlist (effectively being waitlisted for every technical class) and then enrolling in 170 during my july phase 2. 

thanks in advance
history.subject: Safe to phase 2 cs170 in order to get on eecs 149 waitlist?
